          <h2 class="text-center text-uppercase text-black">About</h2>
          <hr class="star-light mb-5">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4 ml-auto">
              <p>Pet Caring is an application to pair owners who are looking for someone to watch
                over their beloved pets with a caretaker. One of the core functionalities that seperates
                this application over other competitors is the fact we allow for owners to big on caretakers
                to get the lowest price. </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 mr-auto">
              <p>Pet Caring is an application built upon Node.js, SQl, CSS, and HTML. The underlying functionalities
                of the application allow any user to register themselves to navigate all given users.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <hr style="height:6px;border:none;color:#333;background-color:#333;" />

